item.title: RellyRell Radio Live Mix New Years Eve Part 1
item.description: Dj RellyRell and Big Tone brought in the New Years real nice mixing live on WNHU 88.7 FM/ WNHU.NET for 5 HOURS STRAIGHT!!! Dj RellyRell was in rare form mixing the very best in Hip Hop, R&B, Reggae, Reggaeton, Oldschool and even some 90s Dance and House Classics!!! This is part 1 of 4 RellyRell Radio goes down at University of New Haven's WNHU 88.7 FM/ WNHU.NET each and every Mondays from 5pm to 6pm and Wednesdays from 4pm to 6pm For more info logon to WWW.MYSPACE.COM/RELLYRELLRADIO WWW.MYSPACE.COM/DJRELLYRELL WWW.WNHU.NET
